metadata.description:
HAPPY NEW YEAR!! 2023 is our year, fam! Let's goooo!! *in Iman Europe's voice*

This is our second drop on Sound.xyz from our duo project. The song is about the thought of a love lost & the pain that is associated with that. We wrote it a few years ago when we realized we couldn't live without each other. We released the official music video for "Without You" as our first NFT ever a little over 1 year ago on Zora, in December of 2021.

Thank you so much for listening, being a part of our journey & collecting. Join our private wavCOLLECTORS' chat:
https://guild.xyz/karmavioletta-and-frens

Written by: KarmaVioletta
Vocals by: KarmaVioletta
Produced by: Karma.wav
Mixed & Mastered by: Karma.wav
Artwork by: Violetta Hyland
